    "id": 12,
    "title": "14 Rules for Faster-Loading Web Sites",
    "type": "BOARD_POST",
    "author": "doortts",
    "authorName": "너굴",
    "created_at": 1209717032000,
    "body": "> doortts | 2008-05-02 금요일 오후 5:30 | Better SW Development | [원본](http://blog.doortts.com/12)\n\n14 Rules for Faster-Loading Web Sites\n\n*   [Rule 1 - Make Fewer HTTP Requests](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-min-http.php)\n*   [Rule 2 - Use a Content Delivery Network](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-cdn.php)\n*   [Rule 3 - Add an Expires Header](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-expires.php)\n*   [Rule 4 - Gzip Components](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-gzip.php)\n*   [Rule 5 - Put Stylesheets at the Top](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-css-top.php)\n*   [Rule 6 - Put Scripts at the Bottom](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-js-bottom.php)\n*   [Rule 7 - Avoid CSS Expressions](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-expr.php)\n*   [Rule 8 - Make JavaScript and CSS External](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-inline.php)\n*   [Rule 9 - Reduce DNS Lookups](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-dns.php)\n*   [Rule 10 - Minify JavaScript](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-minify.php)\n*   [Rule 11 - Avoid Redirects](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-redir.php)\n*   [Rule 12 - Remove Duplicate Scripts](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-js-dupes.php)\n*   [Rule 13 - Configure ETags](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-etags.php)\n*   [Rule 14 - Make AJAX Cacheable](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rule-ajax.php)\n\n참조 : [http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rules.php](http://stevesouders.com/hpws/rules.php)\n\n#### Comments\n\nFaster-Loading Web Sites!!\n오메!\n이런 건 내 분야인줄 알았는데..\n\n [M-o-N](http://nephilim.tistory.com) | 2008-05-24 토요일 오전 1:24\n\n--\n"
